Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這些是綿蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吃掉空氣中的冷氣 長出羊毛一般的毛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以到了夏天總會變多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是今年太多了點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它們是鄰居嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 應該說比較接近生物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過大部分人都看不見它們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對 做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它們的毛很適合製作魔法、魔術相關的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}安潔莉卡也經常找我要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:04:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有多的話 就做成枕頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該會很好睡的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說不定能做你想做的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想做的夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剪完後我想拿點走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要剪腳的部分 剪身體就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 能麻煩早點說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}量還真多 我去拿袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世就繼續練習
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:05:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果有不太一樣的蟲 先跟我說聲再碰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本來想一回來就跟他說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但不知道找什麼時機跟他說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說起來我也不知道要跟他說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}時機 時機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他那麼嚴肅 不會幫我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟他說話有這麼難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟其他的不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲 那隻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼 好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯說碰之前先告訴他的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道碰到會怎樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行 沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}火也沒用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:06:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}繁殖成功了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該回原野了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是雪蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟綿蟲不一樣 會吃曖氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.29,0:07:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它吸走了你身體裡的熱氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世沒有碰它 是它自己撞過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來到夏天的繁殖期 肚子很餓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在得保暖一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經暖多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不如說有點熱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他去巡邏攔住雪蟲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你 我馬上起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不在的時候 我覺得很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但現在這樣和你在一起 卻很溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}時機…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在龍之國怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…很有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有蛇一樣的巨龍潛在河底
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有跳舞的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有在魔法下綻放的花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}林德爾跟我說了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有奈威也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奈威？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們給了我很大的鼓勵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 我看起來好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來你那時醒著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在問林德爾之前 我都以為自己是做夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我純粹只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:09:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:09:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不需要記得這種事 懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為這關係到我很重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.61,0:10:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}絕對不會不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一時衝動真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 你真的不怕我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好像覺得我很害怕你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為在人類看來 我就是很可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也有過家人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有母親 父親 和年幼的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}父母也都能看得見怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們的感情也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然總會有怪物靠近讓我很怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但只要父親在身邊 就是安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然而
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.91,0:11:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有一天父親帶著弟弟離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想母親她可能是累了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以拋下我 離開了人世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我非常喜歡我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但他們都沒有帶我一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以 我原本是…不想再有家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但你卻認我是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他口中的未來永遠不會少了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我覺得 自己能和他走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為是家人 就很想了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:13:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是你什麼都不肯對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以林德爾跟我說你的過去時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很開心？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我怕的不是你 而是怕被你拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類會說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這點我無法否認
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我相信智世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為你是我的徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有了怎樣的感覺 才算是重視一個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.58,0:13:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是怎麼察覺的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.75,0:13:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說過自己很難與人感同身受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:13:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以把你對我說的話說回去 就是撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不在時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得非常冷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 你會如何表達這種感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該是「寂寞」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來是這樣 我寂寞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他的內心果然還只是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只有身體長大了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}買下你真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我又多知道了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那在人類的知識上 我是你的老師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}挺好的 請多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請多指教 魔法老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說起來 我還沒仔細看過你的魔杖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以給我看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 和智世的髮色一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我本來想親自給你最後定型的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定要由別人來定型嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為它也是幫你走過漫長旅途的手杖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以前輩們會給年輕人的魔杖施加祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}祝福他們能順利走完旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我要做第二根手杖的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就拜託艾利亞斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:15:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會耐心等的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你下午有什麼打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.18,0:16:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我打算學魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他還是不肯跟我談他自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不在的時候 有什麼不尋常的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼 也就小鳥飛來嬉戲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是候鳥還是什麼 有點想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先來學習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早 我想要點平時的那種藥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}賽門先生啊 稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接骨木果做的果子露
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這可真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對喉嚨很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恩滋華斯一開始也是給我這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我畢竟是負責監視他的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以前也監視過他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我這喉嚨很壞事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那傢伙很貼心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好喝 還是那個味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼晚了還有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}屋主可在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.01,0:20:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}灰之目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽聞出現了新魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}特此前來祝賀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是個活了上千年的老物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三不五時會來找我交流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他並非人類 你要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放心 我也沒那麼可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}並未想過要傷害你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是遠東之地誕生的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有沙石的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說這髮色 還有那雙眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.44,0:21:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和那島國的人所在的土地 顏色稍有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想必你祖先中 有混雜西方血統的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思 我不太了解我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒關係 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}血緣關係對個體而言 只是小事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類習慣性地會把問題想太深
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明遵從自己的本心就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}向束縛我等的一族人的後裔獻上禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}灰之目！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Comment: 0,0:22:26.98,0:22:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:35.14,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}月は見ていた　欠けてる僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.26,0:22:39.80,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互いを呼び合いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.11,0:22:49.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}遠回りで　遠い道を歩いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.49,0:22:59.60,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}引きよせ合う　赤と黒が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.75,0:23:06.20,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}追いかけ合う　闇と光が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:12.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}二つの対なるもので
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:15.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創られてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.02,0:23:18.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}この世の総べては
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:25.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}あなたがいるから私はいる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:31.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}離れてもそばにいる（そばにいる）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.58,0:23:38.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}誰もが自分の　もう一つの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:44.15,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}片割れという　大切なもの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:52.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}探し続けてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:35.14,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}望著月亮 殘缺的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.26,0:22:39.80,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互相呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.11,0:22:49.31,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}選擇了遠路 並肩啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.49,0:22:59.60,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互相吸引的紅與黑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.75,0:23:06.20,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}相互追趕的光與暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:12.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}對立的兩種存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.57,0:23:15.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創造出了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.02,0:23:18.35,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}世間的芳華絢爛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:25.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只有你在 才有我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:31.58,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我們形影不離（形影不離）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.58,0:23:38.00,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}夢寐以求的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:44.15,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}屬於我們的另一半
